Boys Life 2 is a compilation of 5 short films about being gay in America.Must Be the Music (directed by Nickolas Perry) offers a frank depiction of urban gay youth.Nunzio's Second Cousin finds a gay policeman getting even with homophobic people.Alkali, Iowa (directed by Mark Christopher) chronicles a Midwestern, teenaged gay male who unearths his dead father's secret.The DadShuttle centers on the communication breakdown between a father and his son, who is gay.(*"And if you buy the limited DVD you get the segment titled 'Trevor', starring Brett Barsky")